I graduated HS in '98 and remember watching the first American Pie in the theatre. Apart from it being hilarious and wildly creative, the series features the same actors in all four movies (minus Oz in American Pie 2) and I like how we were able to watch them all grow up. It is cool because I am more or less the same age as the actors and I see so much of the 90s stuff that many will never understand, like having to live without a cell phone, the old way of "streaming" online, the old style web cam, the old pc monitors..... And what a deal! All four movies for under $10! This is great to watch as a marathon on a crappy, winter day, or any "crappy" day for that matter when you need a good laugh.....
This was a great buy for all the four movies. Shipping was fast. Would buy again.
